03-04 September - Hershey Kisses Cookies

1 3/4 cup flour
1 teaspoon soda
1/2 teaspoon salt
1/2 cup sugar
1/2 cup brown sugar
1/2 cup butter or margarine
1/2 cup peanut butter
1 egg
2 tablespoon milk
1 bag Hershey Kisses
1 teaspoon vanilla

Sift dry ingredients in mixing bowl, beat in butter, peanut butter and blend. Add sugar, beat until fluffy. Add egg and vanilla, beat until smooth. Stir into dry ingredients and chill for 1/2 hour. Shape into little balls then roll in sugar before baking. Bake in a preheated 375F oven on ungreased cookie sheet for 10-12 minutes. Remove immediately and top with Hershey Kisses. 